This directory describes how to start building your own castle and add
objects.

If you have any problem, mail them to me: lars@myab.se, or in the
post office in this game (not as good). Please tell me if you would want more
documentation about something.

Files:

RULES			Read these !
general			Easy start.
error			What happens when error.
ed0,ed1,ed2,ed3,ed4	Documentation about ed.
castle			Hints about extending your castle.
std,std2		How to make simple rooms.
door			How to make doors.
monster			How to make monsters.
weapon			How to make weapons.
armour			How to make armour.
quest_obj		For setting up a quest.
